      <example>
         <p>The following markup, for HTML Help output, will produce ....<codeblock>&lt;map title="DITA Reference"&gt;
 &lt;topicref href="anchor.xml" type="topic"&gt;&lt;/topicref&gt;
 &lt;topicref href="apiname.xml" type="topic"&gt;&lt;/topicref&gt;
 &lt;topicref href="audience.xml" type="topic"&gt;&lt;/topicref&gt;
 &lt;topicref href="author.xml" type="topic"&gt;&lt;/topicref&gt;
 <b>&lt;topicgroup  collection-type="family" toc="no"&gt;</b>
  &lt;topicref href="global-atts.xml" type="topic"&gt;&lt;/topicref&gt;
  &lt;topicref href="select-atts.xml" type="topic"&gt;&lt;/topicref&gt;
  &lt;topicref href="univ-atts.xml" type="topic"&gt;&lt;/topicref&gt;
  &lt;topicref href="topicref-atts.xml" type="topic"&gt;&lt;/topicref&gt;
 <b>&lt;/topicgroup&gt;</b>
&lt;/map&gt;</codeblock>
         
         
